{
  "texts": [
    "According to each student's academic history during each semester, the student performance was classified using six classification algorithms (GBT, RF, TE, DT, SVM, and KNN).",
    "The accuracy achieved varied between 90% and 94% for the various classification models.",
    "The positive findings of this study included MSE values of 0.007, MAE values of 0.064, and MAPE values of 1.951.",
    "Research by Liu et al (2022a), used a feedforward spike neural network trained on information gathered from an online learning platform (involving a university in Shenyang) and an educational administration system to predict student grades.",
    "Using pertinent student data and course information, this study investigated the prediction of follow-up grades."
  ]
}